      "chunk_text": "This is a download from BBC Learning English. To find out more, visit our website. Hello, this is 6 Minute English from BBC Learning English. I'm Neil. And I'm Sam. Predicting the future is not easy but that's exactly the job of opinion pollsters – researchers who ask people questions to discover what they think about certain topics.",
