      "apple_rating": 0,
      "chunk_text": "But predicting the future is never 100% accurate and opinion polls don't always get it right. In 2016, few pollsters predicted a victory for Donald Trump over Hillary Clinton in the US presidential election. And in the 2020 US elections, most polls predicted Trump would lose to Joe Biden by a much larger",
