      "chunk_text": "amount than he actually did. These mistakes, sometimes called misfires, when things do not work in the way intended, have damaged the reputation of opinion pollsters. In this programme we'll be taking a look into the opinion polling industry and, of course, learning some useful vocabulary as well. But first I have a question for you, Sam, and it's about another time when the opinion polls got it wrong. Few pollsters predicted that Britain would vote to leave the European Union.",
